unity and product teams and provide strategic advice for how to best utilize Livefyre&rsquo;s and our partner&rsquo;s technology</li><li>Prepare wireframes and assist with SoWs for custom integration work</li><li>Collaborate closely with our technology partners to ensure seamless integrations</li><li>Translate customer requests into thoughtful responses that educate, but also accommodate, customer needs</li><li>Seek feedback on features and measure interest in new products, collect product needs and business goals for new product ideas</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>What things do we look for?</strong></p><ul><li>Deep practical knowledge of social media and online publishing</li><li>Product management experience in a relevant industry</li><li>Analytical, detail-oriented, and creative thinker</li><li>Extensive experience in customer-facing roles</li><li>Experience creating pro-active, strategic digital campaigns</li><li>Team player and ability to collaborate with sales, product, engineering, and external resources</li></ul>]]></description>
